  "recipe_notes": [
    "Maintain oil temperature at 350-375\u00b0F (175-190\u00b0C) for best results; too low and rings will be greasy, too high and they will burn.",
    "Work in small batches to avoid crowding the pot, which lowers oil temperature.",
    "For extra flavor, add a pinch of cayenne pepper or garlic powder to the flour mixture."
  ],
